    <body>
        <p><span class="LIB_Bold">Salutation </span>– If applicable, type the appropriate salutation used with letters in the system. When this field is left blank, the salutation on the letter will use the <MadCap:variable name="Terminology.client_lc" />'s first and last name, and title if one is included on this form.</p>
        <p>For example, if the <MadCap:variable name="Terminology.client_lc" />'s name is Robert Smith and you leave the salutation field blank, letters will start with "Dear Robert Smith," or, if a title is available, "Dear Mr. Robert Smith".</p>
        <p>If a salutation is added, for example Bob for Robert, letters will start with "Dear Bob," instead.</p>
    </body>
</html>